query:
SELECT l.id, l.nome 
FROM lojas l 
LEFT JOIN resultados_mensais rm ON l.id = rm.lojaId AND rm.mes = 12 AND rm.ano = 2025
WHERE rm.id IS NULL
ORDER BY l.nome;
